{"type":null,"faqId":36245,"title":"如何快速截屏？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您可以通过如下两种方式快速截屏：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.2.2.2.2.1.1\"></a><span>同时按住电源键和音量减小键可以快速截屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.2.2.2.2.2.1\"></a><span>滑动状态栏，打开快捷操作面板。点击“截屏”图标即可快速截屏。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"figd0e183\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115627\" style=\"width:3.4729166in;height:2.0854166in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>截图成功后，进入“图库”可查看保存的截图。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<a name=\"gen-id1.2.2.2.4\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115628\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":166,"faqType":"显示与外观","useful":2,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1265","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1438828319000,"seriesProductName":"T1-A23L","visitedTimes":55,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"截屏,截取屏幕,截图","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}